description:
Jonas wants to be an aeronautical engineer.
"I'm going to school," he said. "I have a long way to go but it's something I really want to do!"
Well, he's only 19 so he has plenty of time.
For a young guy, though, he's certainly got a good portion of his life planned out.
"I'm definitely going to get married," he told us. "Three kids, probably, and a couple of chihuahuas!"
Jonas has a lean, smooth, body with a great chest and a nice set of abs.
"I don't really do anything for them," he said. "I've pretty much always had them."
Well, he is 19!
title: Jonas
